actor.name: Satellite
actor.description: This agent is responsible for turning to directions and taking pictures of them.

useCase.name: turn to
useCase.description: The agent satellite turns from an origin direction to a destination direction.

definition.precondition: - the satellite must be pointing to the origin direction; - the satellite must have enough fuel, accordingly to the respective slew time of turning from one direction to the other.
definition.postcondition: - the satellite is pointing to the destination direction; - the satellite fuel is decreased, accordingly to the respective slew time of turning from one direction to the other.
definition.invariants: - the satellite power availability remains the same; - the instruments on board aren't affected.

useCase.name: switch instrument on
useCase.description: The agent satellite switches an instrument off.

definition.invariants: - the satellite keeps pointing to the same direction.

useCase.name: switch instrument off
useCase.description: The agent satellite switches an instrument off.

definition.precondition: - the instrument must be on board of the satellite; - the instrument must be powered on.
definition.postcondition: - the instrument is powered off; - the satellite power is availabe.
definition.invariants: - the satellite keeps pointing to the same direction; - the instrument calibration state doesn't change.

useCase.name: calibrate instrument
useCase.description: The agent satellite calibrates an instrument pointing to a calibration target.

definition.invariants: - the satellite power availability remains the same; - the satellite keeps pointing to the calibration target.

useCase.name: take image
useCase.description: The agent satellite takes an image of a direction with an instrument and saves it.

action.postcondition: s.dataCapacity = s.dataCapacity - data(d,m) and dataStored = dataStored + data(d,m) and haveImage(d,m) = true

action.precondition: s.pointing = dPrev and dNew <> dPrev and s.fuel >= slewTime(dNew,dPrev)
action.postcondition: s.pointing = dNew and s.fuel = s.fuel - slewTime(dNew,dPrev) and fuelUsed = fuelUsed + slewTime(dNew,dPrev)

action.precondition: s.pointing = dPrev and dNew <> dPrev and s.fuel >= slewTime(dNew,dPrev)
action.postcondition: s.pointing = dNew and s.fuel = s.fuel - slewTime(dNew,dPrev) and fuelUsed = fuelUsed + slewTime(dNew,dPrev)

state.name: Instrument powered on without calibration
state.condition: i.powerOn = true and i.onBoard = s and i.calibrated = false

state.name: Instrument powered on with calibration
state.condition: i.powerOn = true and i.onBoard = s and i.calibrated = true

problem.name: Three Satellite 6 Instruments 6 Directions
problem.description: This satellite planning problem has 3 Satellite, 6 Instruments, 6 Directions and 3 modes
